{"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"anchor":"Essentials"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Getting Started with Sloths","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"roleHeading":"Article","images":[{"identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png","type":"card"}]},"kind":"article","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Every sloth has a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". You can optionally provide a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"text":"Create a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of "},{"code":"ice","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wind"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lightning"},{"text":", you can specify this at creation:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator"},{"text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Provide a Habitat","anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Exercise a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol and implementing the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)"},{"text":" method:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Feed a Sloth","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food","isActive":true},{"text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","level":3,"anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Date"},{"type":"text","text":" and an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity"},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted"},"references":{"doc://slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/CareSchedule":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CareSchedule","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"CareSchedule","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CareSchedule","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/careschedule","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A schedule to maintain the health and happiness of a sloth."}]},"doc://slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator":{"kind":"symbol","images":[{"identifier":"slothCreator-icon.png","type":"icon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator","abstract":[{"text":"Catalog sloths you find in nature and create new adorable virtual sloths.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"SlothCreator"},"doc://slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Sloth/power-swift.property":{"title":"power","identifier":"doc:\/\/slothcreatorbuildingdoccdocumentationinxcode.SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property","abstract":[{"text":"The power of the sloth.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/sloth\/power-swift.property","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"power"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Power","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreat